node.text:
I’m completely in love with my new custom made pajamas! 🥺♥️⠀
⠀
You can now get PJs with your own custom pet character on them!! Check out all the different styles at @ohmybrand_official. They’re turning your pups into Disney characters - How cool is that? 😍⠀
⠀
Click the link in our bio now to order yours and don’t forget to enter the code “pokee15” to get 15% OFF your order! 🦔🧡🧡🧡
